The International Handbook of Positive Psychology
A Global Perspective on the Science of Positive Human Existence

Editors: Chang , E.C., Downey , C., Yang , H., Zettler , I., Muyan , M. (Eds.)

    Covers all major regions of the world in the field of positive psychology 
    Provides a coherent framework to get a better understanding of the development and practice of positive psychology
    Offers general directions for future work on positive psychology in global context

